 <h1>New Post</h1>

 <div class="row">
   <div class="col-md-4">
     <p>Guidelines for posts</p>
     <ul>
       <li>Make it sound good, because everyone will see it!</li>
       <li>Don't talk about SupremeA! In fact don't even use the letter "A".</li>
       <li>If you try to use a hashtags you will get banned.</li>
     </ul>
   </div>
   <div class="col-md-8">
     <%= form_for [@topic, @post] do |f| %>
       <div class="form-group">
         <%= f.label :title %>
         <%= f.text_field :title, class: 'form-control', placeholder: "What topic are we talking about today?" %>
       </div>
       <div class="form-group">
         <%= f.label :body %>
         <%= f.text_area :body, rows: 8, class: 'form-control', placeholder: "What do you want to say!" %>
       </div>
       <div class="form-group">
         <%= f.submit "Save", class: 'btn btn-success' %>
       </div>
     <% end %>
   </div>
 </div>
